narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: From this course, I gained the knowledge of several recent theoretical trends in literary and cultural studies, as well as the critical engagement of those theories in the East Asian context.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Strengths: the rather small size of the class allows the discussion to touch very specific and detailed problems, from which I learn a lot.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, I will recommend the class to those East Asian majored student with a strong interest in theory. The overall structure of the class bridges the two issues in a very inspiring way.
